You need to decide whether you&#39;re going to use JUnit 3.x or JUnit 4.x
API. If you&#39;re running on Java 5, I heartily recommend JUnit 4.
Otherwise, your only option is JUnit 3.x.


On 7/17/07, oferstu &lt;oferstu@...&gt; wrote:
&gt;  public class MultiAttacherTest extends TestCase {
&gt;
&gt;  	@Test public final void strongComponenetWalk() {
